divs: Sighting DetailsMe, my Wife,Mum,Dad and Brother were driving home on I95 coming from Orlando heading back to Palm Bay as we had been visiting the parks as my Brother is over from the UK so i was taking pictures of the sun setting and in 1 of them there was a strange object which at 1st i thought was a plane but at the time didnt see any in the distance when id taken the picture. There was nothing in the sky when i looked to see if it was a plane and when i loaded it up to my pc it doesnt help much when i zoom in on the object so im hoping you guys can see what it is!
Summary: I was taking pictures off the sun setting for family back in the UK
